Detroit Tax Auction Sale Prices

Thu 22 June 2017 | tags: assessments, visualizations, -- (permalink)

This map shows the distribution of the average sales price for residential properties sold at the annual Wayne County tax foreclosure auction between 2014 and 2016. I obtained the sales data for 2014 and 2015 directly from the Wayne County Treasurer and I pulled the 2016 data from Loveland Technologies.

Tract values are displayed if you hover your mouse over them. You can also zoom in and out using your mouse wheel if you select the Wheel Zoom feature from the tools on the sidebar.
